B007 added optional smart_turn endpointing (docs/ENDPOINTING.md). The ONNX loader's tensor names and Whisper-feature preprocessing follow the documented upstream pipecat smart-turn v3 contract but were NOT run against a real model export (no model/deps in CI; path is pragma: no cover; any failure falls back to the energy gate). Do NOT test on xsm (not beefy enough) — validate + refine on capable hardware: install the [smart-turn] extra, fetch a real pipecat smart-turn v3 ONNX export, run inference through SmartTurnStrategy, and tune probe/threshold defaults.